title: Madrid and PSG draw in Champions League; City wins late
text:
> Top News Madrid and PSG draw in Champions League; City wins late CSKA's Ahmed Musa gets away from Manchester United's Morgan Schneiderlin during their Champions League Group B soccer match between CSKA Moscow and Manchester United at the Arena Khimki stadium in Moscow, Russia, on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015. (AP Photo/Ivan Sekretarev)
